snippet.title: Wario Land 4: Parallel World (Rom Hack) ver1.0 Release
snippet.description:
Patch Download: https://github.com/becored/WL4_PW

My Wario Land 4 hack, "Wario Land 4: Parallel World" is now completed (ver1.0) and released!
Happy 20th Anniversary to Wario Land 4 🥳

Info about WL4 hacking and other cool mods at Wario Land 4 Hack Vault: https://wario-land.github.io/HackVault/
Join "Wario Land 4 Maker Community Server" discord for info about WL4Editor, update news or giving feedback: https://discord.gg/EQ6JhvP
